I was once told by people I looked up to that I would never make it as an artist and needed to be more practical about my future. I graduated from high school with honors and a full scholarship to college with an emphasis on the musical arts, and STILL...this is what they told me. I had to believe in who I knew myself to be before anyone else would. 

My birthday is in 3 days. All I'm asking for this year is for YOU to be unapologetically you and stand firm in your power⚡️ Be confident. Be genuine. Be kind. Follow your heart and your truth, let it set you free. My life's one goal is to encourage and empower my fellow creatives / creators. 

May 2024 bring you the blessings and abundance you deserve for all the positive energy you put out into the world. 

XOXO -Salty🙏🌈🩷✨️
